sequenceDiagram
  participant U as ユーザー
  participant CLI as Productized CLI
  participant CFG as Config/Profile
  participant EXT as Extension Runtime
  participant PR as Provider Resolver
  participant CAP as Capability Discovery
  participant RT as Agent Runtime
  participant OUT as Output Contract

  U->>CLI: --profile code 修复测试失败
  CLI->>CFG: 解析配置与 profile
  CFG-->>CLI: policy/tools/context/provider/output
  CLI->>EXT: 加载可信 extension
  EXT-->>CAP: 贡献候选能力
  CLI->>PR: 选择满足能力的 provider
  PR-->>RT: provider adapter + model event contract
  CLI->>CAP: 计算本轮 visible set
  CAP-->>RT: visible tools と skill index
  RT->>RT: loop / tool intent / observation
  RT-->>OUT: 结构化事件
  OUT-->>U: TTY 渲染与最终结果
